des:
Users can invoke this skill by saying "open yes two dev".
Then, Alexa will ask the user if he wanna to know information about the company Yes2dev.
If user responds by: tell me more
Alexa will prompt a message.
In other side user can says: good bye or help and Alexa will responds.
priv:
